text:
The pre-teen was singing in a room full of loved ones. J.Lo -- who was front and center -- just so happened to be one of the people she was performing for. When Natasha was finished, Lopez can be seen cheering for her. The star even gave Natasha a high five, before hugging her.

The young singer is definitely brave. We couldn't imagine singing for a global superstar like that -- and at such a young age. Natasha is hands down the MVP!
